JAZ’S WORD: MASTERY OVER NETWORKING 

This is the reason you don’t see me out much.  I spend the majority of my time in the studio somewhere working and perfecting my craft.  There is so much talking going on and no finality and perfection in the product and that’s why there are a lot of people running around with no direction.  It’s fine you can get out there and be seen.  It’s cool sometimes.  but without knowledge and mastery of your craft, you can only get so far 😌☝🏾

Happy Mothers Day Mom, 

You are a beautiful spirit.  Thank you for protecting us and praying over us.  I will always be eternally grateful.  In your life you were never afraid to make changes.  To get up and make a move.  And a lot of that is influenced in me today.  You are so many things.  So many layers in one person. every complex yet soft spoken.  and always pushing to be free in mind body and soul.  Continue to elevate mom.  I love you 😌🙏🏾❤️

50 years around the sun.  A half a century.  I have lived in so many universes.  Met so many people.  And made music work my way.  Even though tragedy is here I have to say I’m happy about where I’m positioned at this point.  Proud of what I accomplished.  And appreciative of what I have. It keeps me young and inspired.  Let’s elevate!! #leogang #birthday #hookmaster 😎☝🏾🚀

Just ME, MY IPHONE, and MY SELFIE STICK: Over the years I’ve been mastering the art of floating my phone with a selfie stick.  Producing a whole song as an artist then going out and shooting the video with just my phone.  It’s a master Jedi challenge.  It keeps me sharp.  And besides, how can I instruct others how to do their thing if I myself can’t do it?  Let’s find innovative ways to create content shall we? ADVENTURES IN PHILLY:  As a San Diego native it’s always good to get out and breath in some different air.  Teleportation to other realms is always helpful to get rid of bad energy, negative vibes, and reset all environments to start off a fresh return.  SD will always be with me but exploring keeps me young.  Philadelphia has so much to absorb and there is an infinite amount to see and do.  There’s 4+ States in close distances to start a side quest at any time.  So much to explore.  Lets elevate 😌🚀☝🏾 #philadelphia #215 #cecilbmooreavenue #northphilly #broadstreet #septa

VARIANT OF MYSELF LONG AGO: E-LUV 95’

I think this was around 95’ or 96’ when I took this.  It’s crazy because I see all these other cats doing it now.  But I was definitely ahead of my time and always dared to be different.  I just didn’t know what to do with all that raw artistic energy.  I was definitely driven and expressive!  Just without the focus i have now!  I still trip looking at this picture! 🤪

I love laying hooks.  And this is a snippet of many I’ve done over the years.
